Serpentor:



Serpentor saw the paw was still coming and with quick resonse time he moved 
his head to the side, the claws digging through his cheek and going out.

Serpentor held in the great gain, anger helping him.  The Alliance robot 
reached into his personal subspace, pulling a vibro-knife out of subspace and 
stabbing it at the wolf's (Luna) neck, the wolf's teeth still in his hand.
